title: 626. Draft Scenarios for Teams Picking 3-5 + Kalani Sitake on Toughness & QB Zach Wilson
itunes:title: 626. Draft Scenarios for Teams Picking 3-5 + Kalani Sitake on Toughness & QB Zach Wilson
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys look at the draft scenarios for the teams currently picking 3, 4 and 5 in the 2021 NFL Draft (3:06). Then, BYU head coach Kalani Sitake joins, as he talks about the culture of toughness in his program, playing through a pandemic, and unique insight into the background and character of BYU quarterback Zach Wilson (15:02). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
